<br>
Remember, you are supposed to be in a coma, so you should not be able to access your gear to swap in regen stuff, and not be able to click any cure poison potions yourself. Maybe code it like when you fall unconscious in the game?<br>
<br>
A compromise for the damage would be random damage each tick from exact normal regen counter up to the point where the guy with 6 AA regen and a fungi still has his HP go down, but slowly.<br>
<br>
So, if something like this came into use, would it be made by a rogue, and used by rogues? (Make it require equiping before you can click it maybe? Or nodrop?) Or would it be made by a shaman and available to all? While I like poisons, I feel this would probably be more likely to be implemented in Alchemy.<br>
<br>
